(144, 41, '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 24pt; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">劳动合同内容达成协议的，用人单位在提前三十日以书面形式通知劳动者本人或者额外支付劳动者一个月工资后，可以解除劳动合同。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">常见<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">用人单位</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">可以解除劳动合同</span>情形：</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">(1)订立劳动合同所依据的法律、法规已经修改或者废止。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">(2)用人单位方面的原因。例用人单位经批准或者根据市场转产、调整生产任务或者变更生产经营项目。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">(3)劳动者方面的原因。例劳动者的身体健康状况变差不适合原岗位工作、劳动能力部分丧失、无法提供所在岗位必要执业证书，造成原劳动合同不能履行或者如果继续履行原合同规定的义务对劳动者明显不公平。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">(4)客观方面的原因。这种客观原因的出现使得当事人原来在劳动合同中约定的权利义务的履行成为不必要或者不可能。俗称为民法中的情势变更。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">双方协商解除劳动合同</span></span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">用人单位与劳动者协商一致，可以解除劳动合同。法律就协商解除劳动合同没有规定实体、程序上的限定条件，只要双方达成一致，内容、形式、程序不违反法律禁止性、强制性规定即可。若是用人单位提出解除劳动合同的，用人单位应向劳动者支付解除劳动合同的经济补偿金。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">劳动者单方解除劳动合同</span></span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">满足法律规定的条件时，劳动者也享有单方解除权，无须双方协商达成一致意见，也无须征得用人单位的同意。主要有两种情况：</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">（1）预告解除：劳动者提前30日以书面形式通知用人单位，可以解除劳动合同。劳动者在试用期内提前3日通知用人单位，可以解除劳动合同。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">（2）任意解除：用人单位以暴力、威胁或者非法限制人身自由的手段强迫劳动者劳动的，当事人可以立即解除且无需通知。</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '180.173.113.36'),
(145, 41, '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">一般来讲，劳动争议仲裁适用&ldquo;谁主张谁举证&rdquo;的原则，特别适用&ldquo;举证倒置&rdquo;原则。在劳动争议纠纷案件中，因用人单位作出开除、除名、辞退、解除劳动合同、减少劳动报酬、计算劳动者工作年限等决定而发生劳动争议的，由用人单位负举证责任。有了这个原则，我们来详细认识下举证规则吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">1、举证责任：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; （1）当事人对自己提出的仲裁请求所依据的事实或者反驳对方仲裁请求所依据的事实有责任提供证据加以证明；没有证据或者证据不足以证明当事人的事实主张的，由负有举证责任的当事人承担不利后果。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; （2）因用人单位作出开除、除名、辞退、解除劳动合同、减少劳动报酬、计算劳动者工作年限等决定发生劳动争议的、与争议事项有关的证据属于用人单位掌握管理的，由用人单位负举证责任。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; （3）在法律没有具体规定，无法确定举证责任承担时，仲裁庭可以根据公平原则和诚实信用原则，综合当事人举证能力等因素确定举证责任的承担。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">2、举证期限：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 承担举证责任的当事人应当在仲裁委员会指定的举证期限内提供证据；当事人增加、变更仲裁请求或者提起反申请的，应当在举证期限届满前提出；因对方当事人增加或变更仲裁请求需要提供反驳证据的，当事人应当在对方当事人增加或变更仲裁请求后仲裁庭指定的举证期限内提供；当事人在举证期限内不提供证据的，视为放弃举证权利，当事人逾期提供的证据材料，仲裁庭审理时不组织质证，但对方当事人同意质证的除外。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">3、质证：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 仲裁庭在庭审中应当组织当事人围绕证据的真实性、关联性、合法性及证明力的大小进行质证，未经质证的证据，不能作为认定案件事实的依据。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">4、证人出庭作证：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 当事人申请证人出庭作证的，应当在举证期限届满前提出，并经仲裁庭许可；证人在仲裁庭组织双方当事人交换证据时出席陈述证言的，可视为出庭作证；仲裁员和当事人可以对证人进行询问；证人不得旁听仲裁庭审理，询问证人时，其他证人不得在场；仲裁庭认为有必要的，可以让证人进行对质，仲裁庭应当对当事人的质证情况记入笔录，并由当事人核对后签名。</span></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '180.173.113.36'),
(146, 41, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>案件简介：</strong><br />\r\n	2013年12月13日我所沈毅芬律师接到易小姐的咨询电话，说自己是某外服公司派遣至A公司的担任会计工作的职工，今天是试用期的最后一天，A公司让她不要去上班了。能不能提起仲裁告A公司。沈毅芬律师答复时机不成熟，建议其马上去上班，如A公司阻止其上班就报警，直到A公司出具书面辞退通知为止。然后再来电咨询。易小姐按照沈毅芬律师的指示在当天就拿到辞退通知，又打来电话问下一步怎么做？沈毅芬律师又建议其到某外服公司报到，直到外服公司出具辞退通知为止。易小姐又如是照做，结果当天也拿到辞退通知。最后易小姐委托我所沈毅芬律师将某外服公司和A公司作为被申请人，以试用期内不符合录用条件解除劳动合同不合法为由向黄浦区劳动仲裁委员会申请劳动仲裁，要求某外服公司支付违法解除劳动合同赔偿金100000元，A公司承担连带赔偿责任。<br />\r\n	<strong>请求理由：</strong><br />\r\n	1)关于违法解除劳动合同的赔偿金。依据《劳动合同法》第三十九条 劳动者有下列情形之一的，用人单位可以解除劳动合同：(一)在试用期间被证明不符合录用条件的;但，员工在试用期内是否符合录用条件的举证责任在用人单位，用人单位必须举证录用的条件、工作要求、业绩考核标准以及考核结果。如果达不到证明要求应该视为违法解雇，应该依法给与赔偿金，计算方式：10000(月薪)*0.5*2倍=10000元;。<br />\r\n	2)关于某外服公司与A公司，谁承担赔偿责任的问题。这是一份劳务派遣式工作。易小姐与某外服签订劳动合同，由某外服派遣至A公司工作，所以在法律关系上，易小姐的用人单位是某外服公司，而A公司只是用工单位。因此沈毅芬律师指导易小姐必须拿到某外服公司的辞退通知，只有这样才能真正拿到&ldquo;违法解除劳动合同&rdquo;的证据。而《劳动合同法》第九十二条第二款规定用工单位给被派遣劳动者造成损害的，劳务派遣单位与用工单位承担连带赔偿责任。因此，由于A公司违法辞退易小姐导致某外服公司与易小姐解除劳动合同的责任应当由二单位连带承担赔偿责任。<br />\r\n	<strong>仲裁结果：</strong><br />\r\n	因某外服和A公司只提供员工手册职位职责说明，无其他证据证明易小姐不符合录用条件，仲裁委员会支持本代理人主张，认为对于录用条件的理解，应该为履行职位职责所必须的年龄、学历、职业资格、技能水平、工作经验等因素，而非员工手册职位职责的描述。员工手册都是概括性语言，没有具体考核标准，因此，单位实际上没有任何有效证据证明易小姐不符合录用条件，属于违法解除劳动合同。</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '180.173.113.36'),
(147, 41, '<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">劳动合同终止后须注意的问题</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">（1）续签合同。企业劳动合同期满即行终止，如生产或工作的需要，可以续订合同，但须双方协商一致；否则，所续订的合同是无效的。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">（2）维持劳动关系，但并未签订劳动合同。由于劳动者法律意识淡薄，劳动合同到期后并未续签劳动合同，仍然继续上班，构成事实劳动关系，但这种劳动关系得不到法律的保护。</span></span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 宋体; background: transparent;"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: medium; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%;">（3）签订合同应符合法律法规的规定。企业在原合同到期后应依照法律和法规办理合同续签事宜，不得出现未经劳动者同意、他人代签等情况。</span></span></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '180.173.113.36'),
